[IBIS Ver]      4.1
[File name]     ibis_v4_1_r_series.ibs
[File Rev]      1.1
[Date]          28/05/2026
[Source]        Artificial data for KiCad QA (issue #24228)
[Notes]         Covers the [R Series], [L Series], [C Series], [Rl Series],
[Notes]         [Rc Series], [Lc Series], [Series Current] and [Series MOSFET]
[Notes]         keywords inside a [Model] block, plus the [On] / [Off]
[Notes]         sub-blocks used by Series_switch models and the component-level
[Notes]         [Series Pin Mapping] table.
[Disclaimer]    This is NOT a valid component

[Component]     SeriesDevice
[Manufacturer]  KiCad

[Package]
R_pkg           50m             40m             60m
L_pkg           2n              NA              NA
C_pkg           10p             NA              NA

