  2     OUT_A           NC               55m      NA      0.2p
  3     IN_B            NC               55m      NA      0.2p
  4     OUT_B           NC               55m      NA      0.2p
  5     IN_C            NC               55m      NA      0.2p
  6     OUT_C           NC               55m      NA      0.2p

[Series Pin Mapping]  pin_2    model_name              function_table_group
  1                    2       series_r
