|
| A series-switch model exercising the [Series MOSFET] keyword.  Single Vds
| table per BIRD 41.8 §5; [On] holds the MOSFET turn-on characteristic,
| [Off] is an essentially-open 1 MΩ resistance.
|
[Model]         series_mosfet
Model_type      Series_switch
C_comp          0pF             0pF             0pF

[Voltage range]   3.3V          3.0V            3.6V

[On]
[Series MOSFET]
Vds = 1.0
|  Voltage   I(typ)    I(min)    I(max)
    0.0V      0.0m       0.0m      0.0m
    1.0V      50.0m      40.0m     60.0m
    2.0V     100.0m      80.0m    120.0m
    3.3V     180.0m     150.0m    210.0m

[Off]
